title: Added support for steps click event
message:
Added support for steps click event

Custom Gesture Detector - to detect click/tap events
Custom steps click areas method - setup the exact click areas for each step
Utility methods for adding/removing/clearing listeners for click events - multiple listeners are supported
JavDoc for added methods, fields and classes - for better understanding the functionality
